name: OrlandoHost Team
notes: Family-owned, full-service Airbnb vacation rental management team serving Greater Orlando, Davenport, and Kissimmee. Grand Welcome affiliate. Handle taxes, guest communications, and maintenance for owners — need reliable cleaning and HVAC vendors. Airbnb-specific focus means fast turnover cleans. Great first call target.

name: Florida Vacation Homes
company: Reunion Vacation Homes Inc. dba Florida Vacation Homes
notes: One of the largest local operators — manages approximately 200 luxury vacation homes in Reunion Resort, Windsor at Westside, Champions Gate, Solterra, Storey Lake, Sonoma. Also services Anna Maria Island. Highest-value potential account: 200 homes x regular cleaning + AC = significant recurring revenue. Also listed on Airbnb and VRBO. Pitch full package (cleaning + AC maintenance schedule). Toll-free: 855-453-5400 / 866-314-7386.

name: Global Resort Homes
company: Global Resort Homes / Global Vacation Rentals
notes: 30+ years in business — one of the most established local vacation rental managers in Central Florida. Serves Kissimmee, Orlando, Davenport, and all Disney-adjacent areas. Also has a Punta Gorda office. Address: 12601 Avalon Road, Winter Garden, FL 34787. Pitch reliability and local service over large national chains. Large portfolio means they need dependable volume cleaning + AC partner.

name: Florida Vacations 365
notes: Tagline: 'We manage your Florida property 365 days of the year.' Year-round vacation rental management = consistent occupancy = consistent cleaning need. Based in Kissimmee. Good size for a startup relationship — not so large that CasaFresh gets lost in the shuffle.

name: PMI Orlando Getaways
company: PMI Orlando Getaways (Kissimmee Property Management Inc.)
notes: Full-service short-term rental management using state-of-the-art tech (Guesty platform). PMI is a national franchise but this is a local operator. They handle inquiries, bookings, check-in/check-out, and oversee cleaning and inspections — meaning they rely on cleaning vendors. Goal: get on their approved vendor list.

name: Steve (KRandPM)
notes: Specializes in luxurious private pool homes 3–7 bedrooms near Disney. Address: 109 Ambersweet Way, Suite 308, Davenport, FL 33897. Smaller boutique operator run by Steve — perfect for direct personal pitch. Pool homes need regular AC maintenance especially during hot Florida summers. Direct email to named decision-maker is gold.

name: ALLSTATES Property Management
notes: Specializes in Kissimmee and Davenport short-term rental management, including the Disney corridor. Advertises maximizing short rental revenue. Contact via form on website. Good target for AC maintenance pitch given Central Florida heat.

name: Orlando Rent A Villa
notes: Full-service vacation rental and property management. Multiple phone numbers suggest a team/office: 863-877-0424 / 863-582-9338 / 863-420-3332. Serves Kissimmee and Polk County (Davenport/Haines City area). Villa-style rentals = larger homes = higher AC load = strong AC maintenance fit.

name: Vibeth Property Management
notes: Expert short & long-term rental management across Orlando, Kissimmee, and Davenport. Modern-looking website and branding — likely a newer operator building their portfolio. Great target for CasaFresh as a preferred vendor from early on. Phone and email both available.

name: Constellation Property Management
notes: Full-service vacation rental management in Orlando-Kissimmee-Davenport area. Gmail address suggests smaller, owner-operated business — great for a personal outreach relationship. Smaller companies often don't have entrenched cleaning vendors and are open to trying new services.

name: Steven (First Light PM)
notes: Launched February 2025 — brand new company. Website is polished and professional. Serves Orlando, Davenport, and Kissimmee. KEY OPPORTUNITY: New companies don't have vendor lock-in. Reaching out early means CasaFresh could become their default cleaning and AC partner from day one. Contact is named Steven — direct personal outreach highly appropriate.

name: Florida Spirit Property Management
notes: Full-service vacation home and investment property management across multiple Central Florida markets: Kissimmee, Davenport, Lake Nona, and Lakeland. Wide geographic coverage = large portfolio potential. Also handles long-term rentals (diversified = more stable client). Contact via email or website form — no phone found.

name: Regal Managers
notes: Vacation home property managers in Kissimmee, near Disney and Universal. Notably bilingual (English and Spanish) — serving international/Latin American investors who own Disney-area vacation homes. Their website has a cleaning services page and maintenance page — they already understand the value and likely outsource this. Contact via website form. Strong pitch: 'We handle cleaning and AC so you can focus on bookings.'

name: Sunnyside / VOG PM
notes: Marketing themselves as the '#1 Rental Company' in Kissimmee. Email domain (vogpm.com) suggests a parent company (VOG Property Management) with Sunnyside as a branded sub-brand. Active operation in the heart of the vacation rental market. Orlando area code 321 = local Central Florida operator.
